                    "company": "MasterPeace",
                    "description": "MasterPeace aims to mobilize 200,000 new peace-builders ('Nelsons') by 2020, working in 200 MasterPeace clubs in 200 communities in around 100 countries. In each community MasterPeace uses music, theater, arts, sports, media, advocacy on the SDG's and dialogue to prevent new armed conflict.   \n\nEach year on the UN International Day of Peace (September 21) MasterPeace organizes peace concerts allover the world to involve local top artists and reach out to the media and recruit new peace-builders, in order to make the movement grow further. \n\nDecember 2013 MasterPeace is awarded by de UN Secretary General Mr. Ban Ki-moon for its peace advocacy work. On Facebook MasterPeace is growing with almost 1000 new fans per day. \n\nMusic above Fighting. Bread above  bombs. Dialogue above judgment. Creation above destruction. That's MasterPeace. \n\nJoin the project by Facebook and www.masterpeace.org\nIn Dutch: www.masterpeace2014.nl \n\nFollow the preparations via Twitter @IlcoMasterPeace @MasterPeace2014\n\nHere's a short documentary about MasterPeace: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DJVRYAC4vVc\n\nYou'll love it. Please share it!",
